23X653_1WQ8_F0002_S_212.title: Re-Nylon playsuit
23X653_1WQ8_F0002_S_212.description: This playsuit with sleek, clean lines is made of Re-Nylon, a regenerated nylon yarn produced from recycled, purified plastic trash collected in the ocean. Technologically innovative fabrics characterize Prada collections, creating cutting-edge designs.
features: Woven nylon tape belt with logo-engraved side-release buckle

VT6060_1ZR3_F0009_S_211.title: Short terry cloth robe
VT6060_1ZR3_F0009_S_211.description: This comfortable, versatile short terry cloth robe is characterized by the elegant contrasting piping and lapels that bring to mind fine tailoring. The enameled metal triangle logo accents the design.

138575_1ZCA_F0480_S_212.title: Oversized jersey hoodie
138575_1ZCA_F0480_S_212.description: The cropped silhouette gives this hoodie sweatshirt a distinctive, sporty character. The garment is lined with Re-Nylon, an innovative regenerated yarn produced from recycled plastic trash collected in the ocean. The tonal fabric logo decorates the garment.

22221_1YMG_F0031_S_211.title: Cashmere fleece pants
22221_1YMG_F0031_S_211.description: These pants with a sporty attitude and soft, cozy feel are made of light cashmere fleece: a luxurious and refined fabric of the highest quality. Inspired by joggers, the design is completed with ribbed knit trim reminiscent of sports uniforms. Prada interprets traditional knitwear in an innovative way, with references to the athleisure world.

P500M_1ZR3_F0009_S_211.title: Terry cloth hoodie
P500M_1ZR3_F0009_S_211.description: This terry cloth hoodie with a contemporary line is characterized by delicate color contrasts that emphasize the zipper closure and the enameled metal triangle logo. The drawstring hem and the soft fabric accentuate the sporty charm of the garment.

P292E_1ZR3_F0009_S_212.title: Terry cloth shorts
P292E_1ZR3_F0009_S_212.description: A sports-inspired fabric and soft design characterize these terry cloth shorts with enameled triangle logo. The interior made of Re-Nylon, a regenerated yarn, enriches the garment with technical details.

P24L1Q_1ZO7_F0008_S_212.title: Cotton crew-neck sweater
P24L1Q_1ZO7_F0008_S_212.description: This cotton crew-neck sweater with ribbed knit motif and slim-fit silhouette has a classic, timeless character. Prada's emblematic triangle logo is transformed into a embroidered detail that decorates the front, while ribbed knit trim outlines the silhouette.

P29972_1Y86_F0002_S_212.title: Wool and viscose turtleneck crop top
P29972_1Y86_F0002_S_212.description: A sportswear-inspired attitude and classic fabrics come together in this viscose and wool turtleneck crop top designed with a front zipper that recalls athletic wear. Presented with coordinated leggings, the plain knit design has a feminine, body-hugging silhouette. The enameled triangle logo adds a delicate element of identification.

22225_1Y86_F0002_S_212.title: Viscose and wool leggings
22225_1Y86_F0002_S_212.description: A sportswear-inspired attitude and classic fabrics come together in these plain knit viscose and wool leggings. The enameled metal triangle logo, an emblematic symbol of Prada collections, embellishes the design.

P26414_1Y86_F0002_S_212.title: Wool and viscose turtleneck sweater
P26414_1Y86_F0002_S_212.description: A sportswear-inspired attitude and classic fabrics come together in this viscose and wool turtleneck sweater designed with a front zipper that recalls athletic wear. Presented with coordinated leggings, the plain knit design has a feminine, body-hugging silhouette. The enameled triangle logo adds a delicate element of identification.
features: Ribbed knit sleeve trim and hem

22226_1Y86_F0002_S_212.title: Viscose and wool Bermudas
22226_1Y86_F0002_S_212.description: These slim-fit biker-style Bermudas inspired by the athleisure world are made of a viscose and wool blend and decorated with the iconic enameled metal triangle logo.

32125_1ZCE_F0480_S_212.title: Jersey joggers
32125_1ZCE_F0480_S_212.description: Characterized by a sleek design with a sportswear mood, these joggers with an elasticized waistband and cuffs are decorated with the fabric triangle logo combined with the sartorial label for a refined signature touch.
features: Fabric triangle logo with sartorial label

39533_1ZCF_F0008_S_212.title: Jersey hoodie
39533_1ZCF_F0008_S_212.description: A sleek design defines the lines of this hoodie. Characterized by a cropped oversized fit, the garment has a sporty mood and is decorated with the fabric triangle logo with sartorial label.
features: Long sleeves with ribbed knit cuffs
Fabric triangle logo with sartorial label

32126_1ZCF_F0008_S_212.title: Jersey joggers
32126_1ZCF_F0008_S_212.description: Characterized by a sleek design with a sportswear mood, these joggers with an elasticized waistband and cuffs are decorated with the fabric triangle logo combined with the sartorial label for a refined signature touch.
features: Fabric triangle logo with sartorial label

P24I1S_1CPC_F0009_S_212.title: Slim-fit superfine wool sweater
P24I1S_1CPC_F0009_S_212.description: This sleek, elegant superfine wool sweater has a refined design that hugs and accentuates the female figure. Superfine wool, a characteristic of Prada's most iconic knitwear, stands out for the fineness, extreme lightness, and exceptional length of its yarn that allows it to maintain its original shape over time. The intarsia logo decorates the product.

P24I1B_1Y1J_F0002_S_202.title: Intarsia shearling and cashmere sweater
P24I1B_1Y1J_F0002_S_202.description: The contemporary design of this sweater blends luxurious materials and elegant, compact knit stitches. The intarsia logo creates a three-dimensional effect on the shearling, while the ribbed knit trim adds a sporty accent to the garment.
features: Deluxe garment with intarsia shearling front

P25I09_1Y1J_F0K74_S_212.title: Oversized cashmere and shearling sweatshirt
P25I09_1Y1J_F0K74_S_212.description: A refined contrast in materials combines plain knit cashmere and luxurious shearling with the intarsia lettering logo. Two fibers with elegant allure blend in an original, hybrid design with an oversized cut that recalls the streetwear world.
features: Garment with shearling and intarsia logo on the front

58A068_1H44_F0002.title: Shearling jacket
58A068_1H44_F0002.description: This jacket stands out for the delicate touch of shearling and the contemporary allure from the original combination of a refined texture and sporty character of the silhouette, with stand-up collar and front zipper closure. The intarsia lettering logo adds a contrasting note.
features: Lined with goose down and feathers

P657OH_1YYM_F0806_S_212.title: Reversible velour coat
P657OH_1YYM_F0806_S_212.description: This coat with sleek, sporty allure is defined by the woven nylon tape belt with buckle, an original and iconic detail of the brand that enhances the silhouette. The reversible fabric and hood give the garment a versatile, technical accent.
features: Reversible garment lined in Re-Nylon Gabardine
Detachable woven nylon tape belt with logo-engraved metal side-release buckle

134642_1Z0I_F0I54_S_212.title: Oversized hoodie with Re-Nylon inserts
134642_1Z0I_F0I54_S_212.description: Complex simplicity emerges from the pure lines of this oversized hoodie that celebrates the emblematic contradiction of Prada collections. Accented with contrasting inserts made of innovative Re-Nylon like the roomy front pocket, the garment blends technical and sporty influences and is decorated with the enameled metal triangle logo.
features: Right flap pocket with strap and side-release buckle

P24G1V_1YMW_F0002_S_211.title: Cashmere and wool Prada logo crew-neck sweater
P24G1V_1YMW_F0002_S_211.description: The Prada logo is presented as an intarsia that decorates this wool and cashmere crew-neck sweater. The sleek, iconic garment has a menswear fit and ribbed knit trim.

29Y955_1WQ8_F0002_S_212.title: Re-Nylon Gabardine down coat
29Y955_1WQ8_F0002_S_212.description: This down coat with detachable hood is made of innovative sustainable Re-Nylon Gabardine, a regenerated nylon yarn produced from recycled, purified plastic trash collected in the ocean, fishing nets, and textile waste fibers. The buckle and the iconic enameled metal logo complete the garment.
features: Woven nylon tape belt with logo-engraved side-release buckle

29Z862_1WQ8_F0002_S_212.title: Re-Nylon down coat
29Z862_1WQ8_F0002_S_212.description: Strong, sleek lines recalling classic tailored coats are reinterpreted in this down coat with a novel character. Prada has always reinvented styles and meanings, creating eclectic combinations that play with the hybrid concept. Emphasized by the wide lapel and voluminous pocket flaps, the design is made of innovative Re-Nylon, produced from recycled plastic trash collected in the ocean.
features: Woven nylon tape belt with logo-engraved side-release buckle
Welt pocket on the front left side
Padded flap pockets with hidden welt

29X992_1WQ9_F0002_S_212.title: Light Re-Nylon safari jacket
29X992_1WQ9_F0002_S_212.description: A hybrid design characterizes this jacket that reinvents the lines of the safari jacket, presenting the classic garment in Re-Nylon, an innovative material produced from recycled, purified plastic collected in the ocean.

291936_1YFL_F0002_S_202.title: Hooded Re-Nylon down jacket
291936_1YFL_F0002_S_202.description: Cozy and warm, this soft down jacket with goose down padding is made of a new sustainable version of nylon, an industrial-inspired material first introduced in the luxury world by Prada. Produced from recycled and purified plastic trash collected in the ocean, Re-Nylon is a technologically innovative regenerated yarn. The garment, cinched at the waist by a belt with side-release buckle, has a detachable faux fur trim around the hood that adds a refined touch.
features: Nylon webbing belt with logo buckle
Hood with fur trim attached by small snaps
Detachable straps attached to the lining at the yoke and under the armholes

58A090_08P_F0002.title: Nappa leather hooded down jacket
58A090_08P_F0002.description: The classic oversized quilted down jacket is reimagined in a new way, presented here in soft nappa leather with a sheen. A study of the triangle inspires new geometric details and unique interpretations of the historic Prada logo. The iconic shape is reinterpreted in the three-dimensional pouch decorating the sleeve of this garment.
features: Lined with goose down and goose feathers
Triangle pouch with logo on the sleeve

52511_1WDV_F0002.title: Nappa leather joggers
52511_1WDV_F0002.description: Sportswear influences blend with unexpected materials to give life to something new, like these joggers with elasticized waistband and cuffs made of soft nappa with a subtle sheen. The emblematic triangle logo of the brand adds an iconic note to the garment.

58A085_1WDV_F0002.title: Reversible nappa leather jacket
58A085_1WDV_F0002.description: The hybrid concept pervades the Prada narrative and results in innovative designs, in an interesting and unusual combination of materials, shapes, and functions. Sportswear influences blend with unexpected materials to give life to something new, like this soft nappa jacket with a sheen, defined by its design with hood, zipper closure, and elasticized cuffs and hem that recall classic sports jackets. The enameled metal triangle logo, Prada's historic code, decorates the garment.

58A095_1WDV_F0002.title: Nappa leather jacket
58A095_1WDV_F0002.description: Sportswear influences blend with unexpected materials to give life to something new, like this soft nappa jacket with a sheen, defined by its design with hood, zipper closure, and elasticized cuffs and hem that recall sports jackets. The hybrid concept pervades the Prada narrative and results in innovative designs, in an interesting and unusual combination of materials, shapes, and functions. The enameled metal triangle logo, Prada's historic code, decorates the garment.
features: Straight sleeve and ribbed knit cuffs

51810_1WDV_F0002.title: Nappa leather miniskirt
51810_1WDV_F0002.description: This straight miniskirt in soft nappa leather reinterprets sporty details in an original way. The front zipper emphasizes the design, which is accented by the nylon belt with side-release buckle, an emblematic detail of Prada collections that reflects the eclectic spirit and duality of the brand.
features: Waistband with belt loop on the back

56A014_1WDV_F0002.title: Nappa leather coat
56A014_1WDV_F0002.description: This coat with urban references and a sleek silhouette is made of soft nappa leather with a subtle sheen. The design draws on sportswear elements like the hood and front zipper closure. The nylon belt with side-release buckle that emphasizes the waist, a recurring detail in Prada collections, is inspired by technical apparel.

51809_1WDV_F0002.title: Nappa leather midi skirt
51809_1WDV_F0002.description: This straight midi skirt in soft nappa leather reinterprets sporty details in an original way. The front zipper emphasizes the design, which is accented by the nylon belt with side-release buckle, an emblematic detail of Prada collections that reflects the eclectic spirit and duality of the brand.
features: Waistband with belt loop on the back

55798_08P_F0002.title: Quilted nappa leather jacket
55798_08P_F0002.description: This jacket in nappa leather, a recurrent material in Prada collections, is characterized by its elegant diamond-shaped quilting. The sleek line enhances its hybrid character, with sophisticated accents and a lustrous sheen. The garment is decorated with the enameled metal triangle logo.

51808_08P_F0002.title: Quilted nappa leather miniskirt
51808_08P_F0002.description: An unusual quilted pattern animates this nappa leather miniskirt that plays with a contrast of semantics and materials. The garments take on unusual connotations: what is ornamental can become functional and what is pragmatic can become decorative. Their essential languages are transformed.

58A091_1ZFE_F0002.title: Oversized nappa leather jacket
58A091_1ZFE_F0002.description: This jacket with masculine lines reminiscent of the biker world is made of nappa leather characterized by its lustrous sheen and texture with vintage allure. The garment is decorated with the enameled metal triangle logo.
features: Straight sleeves and shirt cuffs with snaps

51811_1ZFE_F0002.title: Nappa leather midi-skirt
51811_1ZFE_F0002.description: The sleek line of this high-waisted midi-skirt enhances the texture of fine nappa leather, one of the materials belonging to the brand's heritage. Characterized by a silhouette with retro references, the garment is completed by the enameled metal triangle logo.

58A094_08P_F0002.title: Nappa leather jacket
58A094_08P_F0002.description: A sleek silhouette with a clean, precise cut characterizes this jacket that plays with sartorial and sporty elements, creating an original combination of styles and genres. The shirt collar, which accentuates the straight lines of the design, is combined with a front zipper closure reminiscent of sportswear.
features: Straight sleeve and cuffs with snaps

58967A_1AOI_F0002.title: Nappa leather biker jacket
58967A_1AOI_F0002.description: Essential and timeless, reinterpreted in a slightly oversized silhouette on the shoulders, the classic biker jacket is made of soft nappa leather and accented with Prada's iconic triangle logo, a historic stylistic code of the brand.
features: Straight sleeve and cuffs with zipper
Lower pockets with flap and snap

56A010_1ZAD_F0JHD.title: Shearling coat
56A010_1ZAD_F0JHD.description: An animal print decorates this shearling coat with sartorial lines, classic lapels and welt pockets. The classic design is enhanced by an original element: a detachable nylon gabardine hood that gives the garment a versatile, contemporary soul and recalls the hybrid concept that has always pervaded Prada collections.

58A086_1ZXR_F036S.title: Suede shearling jacket
58A086_1ZXR_F036S.description: This suede shearling jacket features an oversized design with hood and ribbed knit trim. A study of the triangle inspires new geometric details and unique interpretations of the historic Prada logo. Reinterpreted in a conceptual way, the iconic shape becomes a structural element of the garment, turning into a pouch attached to the sleeve and decorated with the enameled metal triangle logo.
features: Straight sleeve and ribbed knit cuffs
Triangle pouch with logo on the arm

58A097_1ZXR_F0K74.title: Suede shearling jacket
58A097_1ZXR_F0K74.description: A timeless design defines this soft suede shearling jacket, emphasized by the contrasting collar and decorated with the enameled metal triangle logo, an emblematic Prada element reinterpreted each season on new contemporary designs.
features: Straight sleeve and shirt cuffs with snap closure
Wide welt pockets on the bottom

138587_1ZXU_F02PL_S_212.title: Oversized studded hoodie
138587_1ZXU_F02PL_S_212.description: Precious elements decorate sports-inspired garments, like this oversized fleece hoodie with front zipper and hood, decorated on the shoulders with studs that create an unusual contrast in texture. In the Fall Winter 2021 collection, clothes take on connotations that differ from the ordinary: what is ornamental can become functional and what is pragmatic can become decorative. Their essential languages are transformed.
features: With hood and drawstring - Ribbed knit hem

132358_1ZXU_F02PL_S_212.title: Studded cotton fleece joggers
132358_1ZXU_F02PL_S_212.description: Precious elements decorate sporty garments like these fleece joggers featuring studs running down the sides that create a unique contrast in materials. In the Fall Winter 2021 collection, clothes take on connotations that differ from the ordinary: what is ornamental can become functional and what is pragmatic can become decorative. Their essential languages are transformed.
features: Elasticized waistband in the same fabric
Elasticized hem in the same fabric

3574AR_1ZXZ_F0009_S_212.title: Cropped studded jersey T-shirt
3574AR_1ZXZ_F0009_S_212.description: Precious elements decorate garments with a sporty soul, like this cropped tee decorated on the shoulders with studs that create an unusual contrast in texture. The Prada T-shirt, an essential garment of the brand, embodies the luxury of simplicity, becoming an attitude and a search to reinvent the basics and propose new meanings.
features: Metal stud embellishment on the shoulders

3557AR_1ZXZ_F0009_S_211.title: Studded jersey minidress
3557AR_1ZXZ_F0009_S_211.description: Precious elements decorate garments with a sporty soul, like this jersey minidress with an oversized fit, decorated on the shoulders with studs that create an unusual contrast in texture. The sleek design recalls the classic Prada T-shirt that embodies the luxury of simplicity, becoming an attitude and a search to reinvent the basics and propose new meanings.
features: Metal stud embellishment on the shoulders

139691_1ZXQ_F0002_S_212.title: Sequined cotton fleece crop top
139691_1ZXQ_F0002_S_212.description: A precious contrast of materials emphasizes this cotton fleece crop top with a hybrid character, accented with dazzling sequins in a play of light and iridescent shimmer. A boxy cut adds a touch of contemporary allure to the garment decorated with the sequin-embroidered logo patch on the back. In the Fall Winter 2021 collection, clothes take on connotations that differ from the ordinary: what is ornamental can become functional and what is pragmatic can become decorative. Their essential languages are transformed.
features: Sequins embroidered on the sleeves and on the triangle logo patch on the back

132358_1ZXQ_F0002_S_212.title: Sequined cotton fleece joggers
132358_1ZXQ_F0002_S_212.description: A hybrid design characterizes these cotton fleece joggers that combine sleek, sporty lines and luxurious details. In the Fall Winter 2021 collection, clothes take on connotations that differ from the ordinary: what is ornamental can become functional and what is pragmatic can become decorative. Embroidered sequins on the triangle logo patch

GFA122_1ZAB_F0008_S_212.title: Organic denim mini-dress
GFA122_1ZAB_F0008_S_212.description: This organic denim mini-dress with a flared silhouette and round neck has a washed treatment that adds a vintage inspired feel. The sleek, sleeveless design features contrasting stitching and Prada's emblematic enameled metal triangle logo.

GFA121_1ZAB_F0008_S_212.title: Organic denim mini-dress
GFA121_1ZAB_F0008_S_212.description: This organic denim mini-dress with clean lines and an oversized silhouette has a washed treatment that adds a vintage inspired feel. The sleek design with a round neck and short sleeves is interrupted by the center seam with contrasting stitching and is accented by Prada's emblematic enameled metal triangle logo.

GFD156_1ZSK_F01CD_S_212.title: Organic denim miniskirt
GFD156_1ZSK_F01CD_S_212.description: This miniskirt is made of organic denim with a treatment that creates a worn-out effect to give it vintage charm. Matching stitching outlines the five-pocket style decorated with the emblematic enameled metal triangle logo on the back.
features: Rounded pockets plus a coin pocket

GFP473_1ZSK_F01CD_S_212.title: Organic denim five-pocket jeans
GFP473_1ZSK_F01CD_S_212.description: These jeans with a high-waist, wide leg masculine cut are made of organic denim treated for a worn-out look that gives them vintage charm. Matching stitching outlines the five-pocket style decorated on the back with the emblematic enameled metal triangle logo.
features: Front rounded pockets with coin pocket

P320L_1ZS8_F0MYE_S_111.title: Striped poplin dress
P320L_1ZS8_F0MYE_S_111.description: Chromatic contrasts and new volumes meet in this poplin dress with summery charm that reimagines the classic sheath silhouette with puffy sleeves and a gathered flounce with a retro mood. A striped pattern gives the design a contemporary look.

GFC036_1ZSK_F01CD_S_212.title: Oversized organic denim shirt
GFC036_1ZSK_F01CD_S_212.description: Streetwear references define this oversized shirt in treated organic denim with a faded effect that gives it vintage charm. Matching stitching outlines the silhouette accented with a patch pocket featuring the iconic enameled metal triangle logo.

P131T_1ZS6_F0I99_S_212.title: Striped stretch poplin skirt
P131T_1ZS6_F0I99_S_212.description: A striped pattern with a retro mood that recalls summer at the beach defines this skirt made of stretch poplin: a cool, light summery fabric. The pencil skirt silhouette features an original gathered flounce that adds a romantic touch.

P3G06_1ZTB_F0MYE_S_212.title: Striped poplin dress
P3G06_1ZTB_F0MYE_S_212.description: Chromatic contrasts and an oversized silhouette meet in this poplin dress with summery charm that reimagines the classic sheath silhouette with puffy sleeves and a gathered flounce with a retro mood. A striped pattern gives the design a contemporary look.

P3G02_1ZTA_F0613_S_212.title: Striped poplin dress
P3G02_1ZTA_F0613_S_212.description: Vibrant color contrasts and references to a summery atmosphere come together in this poplin dress with summer allure that re-imagines the classic sheath silhouette with full puffy sleeves and a retro-style gathered flounce. A play of striped patterns creates original combinations with a mix of warm and cool shades.

P3B74_1ZSY_F0013_S_212.title: Stretch drill minidress
P3B74_1ZSY_F0013_S_212.description: Conceptual in character, this stretch drill minidress has a sleek design defined by its summery charm. Two narrow straps create the slightly squared scoop neck that enhances the flared silhouette, giving it an elegant, modern accent. Prada's emblematic triangle logo is redesigned as a fabric detail decorating the front.

P3G01_1ZSY_F0049_S_212.title: Stretch drill minidress
P3G01_1ZSY_F0049_S_212.description: Conceptual in character, this stretch drill minidress has a sleek design defined by its summery charm. The slightly oversized line reinterprets the classic silhouette of a short-sleeved crew-neck tee, infusing it with new meanings. Prada's emblematic triangle logo is redesigned as a fabric detail decorating the front.

P503M_1ZSY_F0377_S_212.title: Cropped drill jacket
P503M_1ZSY_F0377_S_212.description: A play of contrasting proportions and volumes animates this drill jacket with a straight cropped silhouette that counters oversized details like the large patch pocket on the front and the pronounced shirt collar. The zipper closure adds a sporty note to the silhouette, which is part of a ready-to-wear line and accessories for summer that play with light fabrics and vibrant colors.
features: Sleeves with slits and buttons on the hem
Heat-sealed logo detail on the back

P201FC_1ZSY_F0377_S_212.title: Drill shorts
P201FC_1ZSY_F0377_S_212.description: These colorful shorts feature the iconic Prada triangle logo in a macro version. The design is part of a ready-to-wear line and accessories for summer that play with light fabrics and vibrant colors.

P24L1N_1ZT9_F0049_S_212.title: Oversized superfine wool and viscose T-shirt
P24L1N_1ZT9_F0049_S_212.description: This crew-neck T-shirt that reinvents the classic tee has a sleek, contemporary design with drop shoulder and oversized cut. Defined by its double knit, the garment is made of viscose and superfine wool, a fabric made of extremely fine yarn and characteristic of Prada's most iconic knitwear. The triangle logo is embossed on the front in a delicate tonal detail.

P24L1O_1ZT9_F0016_S_212.title: Cropped viscose and superfine wool T-shirt
P24L1O_1ZT9_F0016_S_212.description: This sleek, elegant crew-neck T-shirt has a contemporary design with drop shoulder and cropped silhouette. Defined by its double knit, the garment is made of viscose and superfine wool, a fabric made of extremely fine yarn and characteristic of Prada's most iconic knitwear. The triangle logo is embossed on the front in a delicate tonal detail.

P433BO_1ZNS_F0363_S_212.title: Double Match silk shirt
P433BO_1ZNS_F0363_S_212.description: The «Dalia» print, one of the most iconic of the brand, decorates one side of this Double Match silk shirt defined by its masculine cut that recalls bowling shirts. Part of Prada's genetic code, recognizable and timeless prints have identified the collections of the brand since the '90s, creating bold combinations or emphasizing designs with traditional allure.

P109MG_1ZNS_F0363_S_212.title: Double Match print silk skirt
P109MG_1ZNS_F0363_S_212.description: This light silk skirt with a fluid design features the «Dalia» print. Part of Prada's genetic code, recognizable and timeless prints have identified the collections of the brand since the '90s, creating bold combinations or emphasizing designs with traditional allure.
features: Side closure with woven tape belt
Sartorial logo label and fabric triangle

35976_1ZSO_F0I99_S_182.title: Striped jersey T-shirt
35976_1ZSO_F0I99_S_182.description: A contemporary character and retro influences meet in this jersey tee with an oversized streetwear silhouette combined with a summery sailor stripe pattern. The Prada jersey T-shirt, an essential item of the brand, embodies the luxury of simplicity, which becomes an attitude and search to reinterpret the basics and propose new meanings.

P261E_1ZWH_F0363_S_212.title: Printed silk shorts
P261E_1ZWH_F0363_S_212.description: The «Dalia» print, one of Prada's most emblematic patterns, decorates these shorts made of soft silk: the light, versatile garment has contrasting piping trim and is completed by the sport detail of the elasticized waist.

P433BO_1ZTG_F0424_S_212.title: Double Match poplin shirt
P433BO_1ZTG_F0424_S_212.description: «Column» and «Stripe», two of the brand's most iconic prints, meet in the Double Match shirt made of poplin and defined by a masculine cut reminiscent of bowling shirts. P202E_1ZNL_F0I99_S_202.description: A stripe pattern that evokes maritime moods with a retro feel defines these shorts made of poplin, a fresh, light fabric that recalls the summer season.

P433BO_1ZTE_F0589_S_212.title: Double Match poplin shirt
P433BO_1ZTE_F0589_S_212.description: «Hibiscus» and «Stripe», two of the most iconic prints of the brand, come together in this Double Match poplin shirt defined by its masculine cut that recalls bowling shirts. Part of Prada's genetic code, recognizable and timeless prints have identified the collections of the brand since the '90s, creating bold combinations or emphasizing designs with traditional allure.

P433BO_1ZNR_F0229_S_212.title: Double Match silk shirt

22H823_1WQ8_F0002_S_202.title: Re-Nylon gabardine trousers

Minimalist lines and modernist simplicity characterize these trousers made of regenerated nylon gabardine. The belt at the waist with buckle comes with a logo-decorated pouch.
features: Waist belt with logo-engraved side-release buckle and nylon gabardine pouch

291831_1WQ8_F0002_S_202.title: Re-Nylon gabardine jacket
291831_1WQ8_F0002_S_202.description: Re-Nylon introduces a sustainable line of Prada products fabricated of regenerated ECONYL®, a nylon made through recycling and purifying plastic collected from oceans, fishing nets, and textile fiber waste. This regenerated nylon gabardine jacket with wide band collar embodies Prada's passion for sports and elegance. Here they meet to create a feminine silhouette accented with sophisticated details such as the pouch applied to the sleeve.
features: Removable nylon gabardine pouch with metal zipper and enameled triangle applied on the sleeve

29B826_1WQ8_F00YE_S_202.title: Re-Nylon gabardine trench coat
29B826_1WQ8_F00YE_S_202.description: Re-Nylon introduces a sustainable line of Prada products fabricated of regenerated ECONYL®, a nylon made through recycling and purifying plastic collected from oceans, fishing nets, and textile fiber waste. This trench coat made of regenerated nylon gabardine is double-breasted and has a belt that accentuates the waist with femininity. Sophisticated details enhance the garment, like the pouch worn at the waist.
features: Re-Nylon gabardine pouch with zipper and enameled triangle logo

P24C1N_1XA3_F0480_S_202.title: Wool and silk crew-neck sweater
P24C1N_1XA3_F0480_S_202.description: This ribbed knit wool and silk crew-neck sweater stands out for its feminine, slim-fit silhouette. The garment is decorated with the Prada logo intarsia on the breast pocket.

P24V0L_1V9P_F0002_S_201.title: Wool sweater
P24V0L_1V9P_F0002_S_201.description: Made of 100% virgin wool, this short-sleeved sweater is decorated with the logo embroidered on the small pocket.

P258C_1XMY_F0480_S_191.title: Light wool trousers
P258C_1XMY_F0480_S_191.description: These light wool cargo pants have an elasticized waistband and hem reminiscent of classic joggers. In its collections, Prada plays with the hybrid concept, combining contradictory elements to create something new and unexpected.
features: Concealed elastic at the waist and hem

P451E_1H51_F0304_S_202.title: Crepe de chine blouse
P451E_1H51_F0304_S_202.description: This straight crepe de chine blouse has classic allure. The garment with front button closure and shirt collar has a patch pocket on the front.

58A025_1XDA_F0002.title: Nappa leather biker jacket
58A025_1XDA_F0002.description: This nappa leather biker jacket is characterized by its antiqued finish obtained through a buffing process by hand, a hallmark of the brand, that creates a three-dimensional vintage effect.

Hand-applied antiqued finish all over the garment
Front closure with logo-engraved metal zipper

P29901_1XA3_F0002_S_202.title: Wool and silk tank top

GFP456_1W42_F0557_S_202.title: Stretch denim five-pocket jeans

The iconic logo label in fine Saffiano leather stands out.

1A0413_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Prada Candy Gloss Edt 30 ml
1A0413_ZX2_F0Z99.description: An explosion of joy, Prada Candy gloss is a sensual sorbet, sweet as acid cherry and solar as the orange blossom. A fruity bouquet with hints of rose and musk with a feminine and bright attitude.
features: Blended by Daniela Andrier under the creative direction of Miuccia Prada, Prada Candy Gloss represents the idea of a multi-layered coating of olfactory notes, each one rendering the overall experience shinier and more feminine. The starting point and core of the perfume is the sweet bass note, where enticing vanilla-like almond is infused with the sensual tenderness of musk, then encased in another sweet lustrous texture, to create an olfactory sensation akin to a pastel pink, sugared almond dragée. In turn, this accord is further cocooned within a bright cherry top note, its zest and sweetness interacting like a fresh sorbet, and given further lightness with the presence of the orange blossom's uplifting nuances within the fragrance's heart.

1A0421_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Smells of leather, agarwood and tobacco surround an heart, delicate yet potent, of Rose Absolute and Patchouli. Miracle of the Rose is a sensation of a passage through multiple, labyrinthine rooms, each is infused with a different scent.
features: A deep, dark base of vanilla, nutmeg, cinnamon, pimento and cumin gets along with ylang ylang, peach and sophisticated essences of sandalwood. Soleil au Zenith is an overload of sensation, the discovery of multiple cultures.

1A0422_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories Les Mirages - Soleil Au Zenith EDP 100 ml
1A0422_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A deep, dark base of vanilla, nutmeg, cinnamon, pimento and cumin gets along with ylang ylang, peach and sophisticated essences of sandalwood. Soleil au Zenith is an overload of sensation, the discovery of multiple cultures.

1A0423_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories Les Mirages - Dark Light EDP 100 ml
1A0423_ZX2_F0Z99.description: The warmth of amber and the cool cleanliness of aldehydes, Dark Light is a mix of synthetic and natural notes. The components are older than memory: Musk, Madagascar vanilla, Myrrh, Angelique and the deeply complex aura of opoponax gum.
features: Notes: Amber, Aldehydes, Musk, Vanilla from Madagascar, Myrrh, Angelica and Opoponax gum resin

1A0105_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Prada Amber Pour Femme EDP deluxe 80 ml
1A0105_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Distinctive, intimate, sumptuous, Prada Amber Pour Femme Eau de Parfum Deluxe is hypnotic, unique and evocative. This fragrance is «A new way to wear Prada”, re-exploring the spirit of amber in four characteristic ways: sandalwood oil from India, patchouli leaves from Indonesia, labdanum resin from France and benzoin from Siam.
features: Notes: Bergamot Oil Italian, Bitter Orange Oil, Mandarin Oil Sicily, Mimosa Absolute, Patchouli, Rose Absolute, Schinus Molle Absolute, Patchouli Oil Indonesia, Labdanum Resinoide, Tonka Bean Absolute, Vanilla Absolute, Sandalwood Oil India, Benzoin Siam Resinoide

1A0337_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Cargo De Nuit EDP 100 ml
1A0337_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Inspired by the mystery of a night voyage in the ocean, Cargo de Nuit opens with soft notes of Musk and Aldehydes that crash into woody and mineral notes.
features: Heart notes: Woody and mineral notes

1A0338_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Day For Night EDP 100 ml
1A0338_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A modern encounter with ancient nature, Day For Night is a fragrance that opens with Styrax and Patchouli's notes, it warms to a rich Amber core powdery, woody and softly sweet, that gives way to a strong yet smooth blend of Musk and Leather.
features: Notes: Styrax, Patchouli, Amber, Musk and Leather

1A0339_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Heat Wave EDP 100 ml
1A0339_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Heat Wave is an exotic holiday, a voyage to an island at night... A trip that begins with the sweet Ylang-Ylang and Davana's notes, continues with the floral explosion of Tuberose and Datura, finishing with sweet Frangipani and Vanilla.
features: Notes: Ylang-Ylang, Davana, A fleshy, floral heart of Tuberose and Datura, Frangipani and Vanilla

1A0340_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Pink Flamingos EDP 100 ml
1A0340_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Natural and synthetic elements combine to create a fragrance that is an imaginary fantasy, a cloud of pink bubbles. Pink Flamingos opens with citrus, continues with Cherry accord softened with Rose and Iris, leaving traces of powder, sugar and Musk.
features: Notes: Citrus, Cherry accord softened with Rose

1A0378_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion d'Iris Cedre EDP 100 ml
1A0378_ZX2_F0Z99.description: An unusual interpretation of the queen Iris, a citrus and woody fragrance with a very powerful energy. Iris Cèdre walks a tonal tightrope between the evocative notes of Iris and Neroli, Cedarwood, Vetiver, Incense and Benzoin.
features: Accord, Orris, Cedarwood, Vetiver, Benzoin, Incense

1A0379_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion de Fleur D'Oranger EDP 100 ml
1A0379_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A delicate and charming fragrance with the orange blossom absolute, neroli and the luxurious and voluptuous Jasmine. A fresh and irreverent parfum emphasized by sparkling Mandarin water.
features: Notes: Tunisian Neroli, Jasmine, Lily of the

1A0380_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion d'Amande EDP 100 ml
1A0380_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Inspired by the oriental mood, Amande is a rich fragrance characterized by notes of almond infused in a bergamot water. Anisic notes and spicy floral are the heart notes, tonka beans for the base notes and citrus and bitter almond, the top notes.
features: Notes: Italian Mandarin and Bitter Almond, Star Anise and Heliotrope, Tonka Bean and Musk

1A0381_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion d'Oeillet EDP 100 ml
1A0381_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Sensual and fresh this spicy floral fragrance is a mix of sandalwood, mandarin essence and Hinduran Styrax. Oeillet is a dream of memories with an intense and voluptuous allure.
features: Notes: Italian Mandarin, Sandalwood, Patchouli, Styrax

1A0382_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion de Vetiver EDP 100 ml
1A0382_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Fresh, spicy and woody with the Vetiver impressive touch. An elegant confrontation of tradition and modernity with a poetic interpretation, Vetiver is a reminiscent of a very tender kind of green.
features: Notes: Italian Bergamot, Italian Mandarin, Lime, Cardamome, Tunisian Neroli, Turkey

1A0383_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Double Dare EDP 100 ml
1A0383_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A place beyond charted territory... Double Dare is a fragrance inspired by the know-how of the legendary Prada leather goods, with a spicy opening with Saffron and Cardamom notes, an heart of creamy Suede – an imaginary note created by the perfumer – and Jasmine, finishing with the warm and sensual alliance of Vanilla, Vetiver and Ambergris.
features: Notes: Saffron and Cardamom, Jasmine, The smooth alliance of Vanilla, Vetiver and Ambergris

1A0384_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Purple Rain EDP 100 ml
1A0384_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Purple Rain is a reworking of the Prada's iconic Iris scent. The fragile perennial becames an opulent bloom. The intoxicating encounter of fresh and dry notes blended with Iris as a link between land and sky, heaven and humanity. Purple Rain opens with fresh and green notes of Neroli, warmed from Iris and Orange Blossom, then gives way to the dry freshness of Vetiver.
features: notes blended with Iris, Orange Blossom, Vetiver

1A0385_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Marienbad EDP 100 ml
1A0385_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Elegant and decadent, Marienbad is a baroque and distinguished fragrance, with vanilla top notes, an heart of Incense and Styrax and base notes of musky Amber.

1A0386_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Nue Au Soleil EDP 100 ml
1A0386_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Intense and inebriating, Nue au Soleil is a golden nectar, exploding from a flower. The intensity of a unique Orange Blossom. The fragrance opens with the lightness and freshness of Neroli then intensifies to a sensual core of Orange Blossom, enhanced with Patchouli and Musks.
features: Notes: Orange Blossom, Neroli, Patchouli and Musk

1A0387_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Tainted Love EDP 100 ml
1A0387_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Tainted Love eau de parfum shows seductive side to Prada with playful synthetic lipstick tones, designed to invoke a sense of glamour. 1A0388_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Un Chant d'Amour EDP 100 ml
1A0388_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Un Chant d'Amour is the fragrance of the human essence, seductive, intimate and carnal. Neroli combines with a touch of seducing orange blossom and powdery and sensual Musks.

features: Notes: Citrus, Cherry accord softened with Rose

1A0378_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion d'Iris Cedre EDP 100 ml
1A0378_ZX2_F0Z99.description: An unusual interpretation of the queen Iris, a citrus and woody fragrance with a very powerful energy. Iris Cèdre walks a tonal tightrope between the evocative notes of Iris and Neroli, Cedarwood, Vetiver, Incense and Benzoin.
features: Accord, Orris, Cedarwood, Vetiver, Benzoin, Incense

1A0379_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion de Fleur D'Oranger EDP 100 ml
1A0379_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A delicate and charming fragrance with the orange blossom absolute, neroli and the luxurious and voluptuous Jasmine. A fresh and irreverent parfum emphasized by sparkling Mandarin water.
features: Notes: Tunisian Neroli, Jasmine, Lily of the

1A0380_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion d'Amande EDP 100 ml
1A0380_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Inspired by the oriental mood, Amande is a rich fragrance characterized by notes of almond infused in a bergamot water. Anisic notes and spicy floral are the heart notes, tonka beans for the base notes and citrus and bitter almond, the top notes.
features: Notes: Italian Mandarin and Bitter Almond, Star Anise and Heliotrope, Tonka Bean and Musk

1A0381_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion d'Oeillet EDP 100 ml
1A0381_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Sensual and fresh this spicy floral fragrance is a mix of sandalwood, mandarin essence and Hinduran Styrax. Oeillet is a dream of memories with an intense and voluptuous allure.
features: Notes: Italian Mandarin, Sandalwood, Patchouli, Styrax

1A0382_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion de Vetiver EDP 100 ml
1A0382_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Fresh, spicy and woody with the Vetiver impressive touch. An elegant confrontation of tradition and modernity with a poetic interpretation, Vetiver is a reminiscent of a very tender kind of green.
features: Notes: Italian Bergamot, Italian Mandarin, Lime, Cardamome, Tunisian Neroli, Turkey

1A0383_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Double Dare EDP 100 ml
1A0383_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A place beyond charted territory... Double Dare is a fragrance inspired by the know-how of the legendary Prada leather goods, with a spicy opening with Saffron and Cardamom notes, an heart of creamy Suede – an imaginary note created by the perfumer – and Jasmine, finishing with the warm and sensual alliance of Vanilla, Vetiver and Ambergris.
features: Notes: Saffron and Cardamom, Jasmine, The smooth alliance of Vanilla, Vetiver and Ambergris

1A0384_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Purple Rain EDP 100 ml
1A0384_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Purple Rain is a reworking of the Prada's iconic Iris scent. The fragile perennial becames an opulent bloom. The intoxicating encounter of fresh and dry notes blended with Iris as a link between land and sky, heaven and humanity. Purple Rain opens with fresh and green notes of Neroli, warmed from Iris and Orange Blossom, then gives way to the dry freshness of Vetiver.
features: notes blended with Iris, Orange Blossom, Vetiver

1A0385_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Marienbad EDP 100 ml
1A0385_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Elegant and decadent, Marienbad is a baroque and distinguished fragrance, with vanilla top notes, an heart of Incense and Styrax and base notes of musky Amber.

1A0386_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Nue Au Soleil EDP 100 ml
1A0386_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Intense and inebriating, Nue au Soleil is a golden nectar, exploding from a flower. The intensity of a unique Orange Blossom. The fragrance opens with the lightness and freshness of Neroli then intensifies to a sensual core of Orange Blossom, enhanced with Patchouli and Musks.
features: Notes: Orange Blossom, Neroli, Patchouli and Musk

1A0387_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Tainted Love EDP 100 ml
1A0387_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Tainted Love eau de parfum shows seductive side to Prada with playful synthetic lipstick tones, designed to invoke a sense of glamour. A unique juxtaposition of synthetic notes: an opening of Raspberry, an heart of Rose and powdery Violet, and a touch of sensual traces of Musks.
features: Notes: Raspberry, Notes of Rose and powdery Violet, Musk

1A0388_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories - Un Chant d'Amour EDP 100 ml
1A0388_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Un Chant d'Amour is the fragrance of the human essence, seductive, intimate and carnal. Neroli combines with a touch of seducing orange blossom and powdery and sensual Musks.

1A0406_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion de Mimosa EDP 100 ml
1A0406_ZX2_F0Z99.description: The golden spheres of Mimosa infuse their powdery fragrance, blended with the freshness of Mandarin essence. A very fresh and floral perfume, an expression of joy and serene state of being.
features: Notes: Mimosa Absolute, Star Anise, Rose Absolute Strawberry, Heliotrope Musk

1A0424_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories Les Mirages - Midnight Train EDP 100 ml
1A0424_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A memory, a travel through wandering lands, Midnight Train is a mix of sweet Texan cedarwood, woody Andalusian cistus, and Indonesian patchouli swirling around a bright, warm Amber accord.
features: Notes: Citron, Indonesian Patchouli, Citrus fruits, Amber

2A0207_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Prada Amber Pour Homme Edt 100 ml
2A0207_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A rich, complex amber intermingles with the clean, fresh scent of barber's soap, typical of a fougère, Amber man is the first fragrance for man signed Prada, a synchrony of olfactory contrasts: Fresh vs. Sensual and Clean vs. Leathery.
features: Notes: Cardamom from Guatemala, Mandarin and Bergamot from Italy, Geranium from Africa, Vetiver and Neroli, Labdanum from France, Patchouli from Indonesia, tonka Bean and Vanilla

2A0208_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Prada Amber Pour Homme Edt 50 ml
2A0208_ZX2_F0Z99.description: It’s Prada's first men’s fragrance, a distinctive interpretation of the classic fragrance of tomorrow and a continuation of the fragrance narrative that began with Prada’s first female fragrance, emerging as “chapter two” in the layered, alluring story of Amber fragrances. With its highly natural but seductive charm, Prada makes and leaves a lasting impression. A rich, complex Amber intermingles with the clean, fresh scent of barber’s soap, typical of a fougère, and continues to evolve between a duet of olfactory contrasts.
features: Top notes: Mandarin, Neroli, Bergamot, Cardamom
Heart notes: Orange Blossom, Musk, Vetiver, Geranium, Myrrh
Base notes: Labdanum, Leather, Sandalwood, Tonka Bean, Patchouli, Vanilla, Saffron

2A0251_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Prada Amber Pour Homme Intense EDP 100 ml
2A0251_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A rich, complex amber intermingles with the clean, fresh scent of barber's soap, typical of a fougère, Amber man is the first fragrance for man signed Prada, a synchrony of olfactory contrasts: Fresh vs. Sensual and Clean vs. Leathery.
features: Notes: Cardamom from Guatemala, Mandarin and Bergamot from Italy, Geranium from Africa, Vetiver and Neroli, Labdanum from France, Patchouli from Indonesia, tonka Bean and Vanilla

2A0263_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Prada Luna Rossa Sport Edt 50 ml
2A0263_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A Sensual, spicy, amber fragrance with vibrant lavender and explosive ginger and juniper berries. Tobacco, tonka beans and vanilla are the base notes, Luna Rossa Sport express the pulsing spirit of a boat racing with a powerful explosion of vitality.
features: Notes: Lavender Juniper Berries Ginger, Iris accord Hay, Tonka Beans Vanilla Heliotrope Musk

2A0275_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Prada Luna Rossa Black 50 ml
2A0275_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Prada Black starts with vivacious notes of Bergamot and Angelica, arriving at the sweetness of Amber Wood passing through the intensity of Coumarin and Patchouli. Even the completely opaque bottle, where the iconic red line was replaced for the very first time by a black one, denotes the strength and intensity of this new Eau de Parfum.
features: Notes: bergamot, angelica, amber wood, coumarin, patchouli.

2A0277_ZX2_F0Z99.title: L'Homme Prada L'Eau Edt 50 ml
2A0277_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Amber and Iris blend with Red Ginger and Neroli. Fresh green notes create an irresistible, sensuous contrast on a sandalwood base. A floral note, made even more persistent, accentuates the sensation of freshness, while the presence of sandalwood attenuates cedar wood and chypre scents. This new interpretation of freshness comes in a silver-tone metal bottle with pale blue Saffiano leather bearing the original Prada logo.
features: Notes: amber, iris, ginger, neroli, sandalwood, cedar wood.

2A0278_ZX2_F0Z99.title: L'Homme Prada L'Eau Edt 100 ml
2A0278_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Amber and Iris blend with Red Ginger and Neroli. Fresh green notes create an irresistible, sensuous contrast on a sandalwood base. A floral note, made even more persistent, accentuates the sensation of freshness, while the presence of sandalwood attenuates cedar wood and chypre scents. This new interpretation of freshness comes in a silver-tone metal bottle with pale blue Saffiano leather bearing the original Prada logo.
features: Notes: amber, iris, ginger, neroli, sandalwood, cedar wood.

2A0279_ZX2_F0Z99.title: L'Homme Prada L'Eau Edt 150 ml
2A0279_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Amber and Iris blend with Red Ginger and Neroli. Fresh green notes create an irresistible, sensuous contrast on a sandalwood base. A floral note, made even more persistent, accentuates the sensation of freshness, while the presence of sandalwood attenuates cedar wood and chypre scents. This new interpretation of freshness comes in a silver-tone metal bottle with pale blue Saffiano leather bearing the original Prada logo.
features: Notes: amber, iris, ginger, neroli, sandalwood, cedar wood.

1A0439_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Infusion de Mandarine EDP 100 ml
1A0439_ZX2_F0Z99.description: Infusion de Mandarine is the first citrusy fragrance of the collection. The infusion is not a distillate but a reconstruction of the essence of tangerine and orange, a formula designed to stimulate complex emotions inspired by a segment of the first fresh tangerine of the season. The fragrance opens with head notes of bitter orange and a bittersweet touch of vert de mandarine. At the heart of the fragrance, orange blossom absolute meets neroli essence, contrasting with the passionate notes of opoponax.
features: Notes: Bitter orange, vert de mandarine, orange blossoms, neroli essence, opoponax

1A0443_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories Les Mirages - Desert Serenade EDP 100 ml
1A0443_ZX2_F0Z99.description: An elegantly dark scent of Honey and Leather that changes with Saffron notes.

1A0444_ZX2_F0Z99.title: Olfactories Les Mirages - Moonlight Shadow EDP 100 ml
1A0444_ZX2_F0Z99.description: An intense, fruity Leather base attenuated by Fig and Cedar Wood.

2A0281_ZX2_F0Z99.title: L'Homme Prada Absolu EDP 100 ml
2A0281_ZX2_F0Z99.description: A subversive signature Iris heart, contrasted with fresh citric notes of Bergamot and Mandarin at the top, challenged and given depth by Cedar wood and the amber accents of black Pepper at the fragrance's finish.

2A0282_ZX2_F0Z99.title: L'Homme Prada Watersplash 150 ml
2A0282_ZX2_F0Z99.description: L’Homme Prada Watersplash, at once refreshing and indulgent, explores the fluid space between polar definitions, rejecting cliché conventions to forge new realities. In the fragrance, fresh cut Ginger and airy Neroli are layered upon dry Cedar and Sandalwood.

2A1156_2D00_F0Z99_P_ML050.title: Luna Rossa Ocean EDT 50 ml
2A1156_2D00_F0Z99_P_ML050.description: Formulated by IFF Master Perfumers Anne Flipo and Carlos Benaim, Prada Luna Rossa Ocean has a unique neo-fresh olfactory signature that reinvents the emblematic fougère family. Sublimating notes of aromatic freshness mixed with the sophisticated sensuality of bergamot, a contrast is created with the sophisticated essence of vetiver. Everything intertwines in the heart notes with an elegant iris accord. The fragrance unveils a luminous cocktail of citrus combined with a lively duo of lavender and sage to add a fresh, clean sensation. The unique leather heart creates a second skin effect, exploring a sensual accord of suede and saffron combined with the elegant creamy notes of iris root. Enveloped in a masterful blend of patchouli, Haitian vetiver and musks, the fragrance leaves an addictive and masculine scent.
features: Top notes: Bergamot, Pink Pepper, Artemisia
Heart Notes: Iris Notes, Lavender, Saffron Accord
